nodes.text: Min was a female Human living in the Neebray Garrison on Balmorra during the Cold War. She asked an Imperial not to destroy a power generator on which she and other Balmorran refugees depended.
Min is a non-player character from the massively multi-player online role playing video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, which was released by BioWare in 2011. She is voiced by Jennifer Hale.
